"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-12-will-next-olympics-held-2028-2032-host-cities-21403922\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"TheParis2024Olympicsmay have only just finished but already anticipation is building for the nextsummerGames.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is just 18 months to go before the next edition of theWinter Olympicswhich is being held in the Italian cities ofMilanand\\u00a0Cortina d'Ampezzo in 2026.\", \"from\": 111, \"to\": 265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 213, \"end\": 220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9841675000841015, \"rank\": 0.0158960724385439, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cortina d'Ampezzo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cortina_d'Ampezzo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if athletics, gymnastics, swimming, cycling and everything in between is more your thing then you have going to have to be a little patient.\", \"from\": 267, \"to\": 411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So where and when will the next Olympics take place?\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 465, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And what about the Games after that?\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's what you need to know:  The 2028 Olympic Games will be held inLos Angeles, California, in theUnited States of America.\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 585, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9890861135874797, \"rank\": 0.011017675214808152, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee confirmedLA had won their bid to stage the Gamesback in September 2017, at the same time that 2024 Games were awarded to Paris.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 634, \"end\": 665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 787, \"end\": 792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992924131, \"rank\": 7.075460865438068e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both cities had wanted to host the 2024 event, before LA agreed to wait an extra four years after the IOC made guarantees on funding.\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.530132947983834e-30, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will be the fifth time that the summer Olympics have been held in the US and the third time in LA after 1932 and 1984.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9346676059434335, \"rank\": 0.04771952869683331, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"St. Louis and Atlanta played host in 1904 and 1996 respectively.\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999999997965006, \"rank\": 1.7053938534114837e-10, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will therefore make LA the third city to have hosted three Olympic games afterLondonand Paris.\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1209, \"end\": 1214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992924131, \"rank\": 7.075460865438068e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The closing ceremony in Paris saw the official handover of the Games to the Californian city, witha little help from Tom Cruiseand Snoop Dog.\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1241, \"end\": 1246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992924131, \"rank\": 7.075460865438068e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1348, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dog\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tbrowser thatsupports HTML5 \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tvideo  Up Next  To get the latest news from the capital, visit Metro'sLondon news hub.